      <div class="info">
        <div class="info-text">
          <h2>more about us</h2>
          <p>
            Our project aims to address the issue of food wastage in restaurants
            by creating a web application that facilitates the sharing and
            redistribution of surplus food. Restaurants often have excess food
            at the end of the day that goes to waste. Our platform allows
            restaurants to register and list their surplus food donations.
            Organizations dedicated to food redistribution are notified to
            collect and distribute the surplus food, reducing wastage and
            helping those in need.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
